lemma disjoint_bind': "\<And>S T f g. (\<And>s t. s \<in> S \<and> t \<in> T \<Longrightarrow> f s \<inter> g t = {}) \<Longrightarrow> (S \<bind> f) \<inter> (T \<bind> g) = {}"
by (auto simp: bind_UNION)
